$ curl -X POST &amp;#34;https://app.brightsec.com/api/v1/files?discard=true&amp;#34; \ -H &amp;#34;Content-Type: multipart/form/data&amp;#34; \ -H &amp;#34;Authorization: Api-Key API_KEY&amp;#34; \ -f &amp;#39;har=@//path/to/the/file.har&amp;#34; The response id will then be used during setting a new scan in the pipeline, for example:
